{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Echoes of Spellcraft</strong></i> is a single-player game that combines the strategic depth of roguelike deck-building with the thrill of real-time dynamic combat.\u00a0Play powerful spells at the right moment, encounter different events, and adopt unique strategies in each game to defeat endless waves of enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/\u6807\u9898\u56fe.png?t=1737710644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/hf_y_1.png?t=1737710644\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The protagonist automatically seeks out and attacks the nearest enemy.  <br>All you need to do is drag and drop spells at the right moments to unleash them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/Battle.gif?t=1737710644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/hf_y_2.png?t=1737710644\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Casting spells increases your Heat, which will gradually decrease over time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But be careful\u2014casting too many spells will lead to Overload, preventing you from casting any spells until fully cooled down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/Overload.gif?t=1737710644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/hf_y_3.png?t=1737710644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Treasure, shops, facing elite monsters, or exploring the unknown\u2014the choice is yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/Mist.gif?t=1737710644\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/hf_y_4.png?t=1737710644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Synthesize basic spells into higher-level ones, or maintain specific spell combinations to trigger additional synergy effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/Spell.gif?t=1737710644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/hf_y_5.png?t=1737710644\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100+ meticulously designed spells, 50+ unique enemies, 8 different hero abilities, along with various events and relics are all waiting for you to explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/More.gif?t=1737710644\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sorcery Priest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152290/765e39013a557ba8017f6c5dcd70573ba2f1a9c9.jpg"},{"name":"Shadow Dominator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152290/d793157fa56afe07dd0ad2884708735cb634a3ff.jpg"},{"name":"Unicorn Monarch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152290/7d0659d9353b37b60716d2fe3dba46040956d50a.jpg"},{"name":"Mysterious stranger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pub